title: 2022 March Madness Pick Em Round of 64
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for the first round of March Madness. The boys air out their grievances before a long weekend of streaming all 32 games of the Tournament.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
